<A Place Holder Folder Synced with Guest VM-Workstation>
Mapping: workspace/chef_repo (HostPC)
         /home/vagrant/chef-starter/chef_repo(Guest PC i.e Workstation)

Benefits of Using This :

We can do add/edit/update the recipe using our local machine and using an IDE (Code Studio) and it will sync automaticly.
So, We can paste the contain of che-starter/chef-repo in this folder i.e workspace/chef-repo



